{"tid":1536502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［快閃］關於快閃有啲建議","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T03:19:21.000Z","uid":15362,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"578c6be6cd6c7742dabcde54882613bce04ec0ff","tid":1536502,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"第一. 大家快閃首先要有目的性例如 燒狗屋 扑狗鐵 做完即閃 唔好等班狗支援黎先走 佢地叫人時間大概15-30分鐘 所以去到睇完情況可行 即刻行動 之後就閃 純粹想撚狗唔該街坊裝去 你full gear去佢一定射你捉你唔洗諗<br />\n<br />\n第二. 設定好用腳走既逃生路線 呢幾日可以睇到地鐵又好 巴士又地班狗隨時都可以沖入去 所以唔好再依賴交通工具 <br />\n想換裝去到公屋樓下開遮換裝 又搵地方坐車走<br />\n<br />\n第三. 哨兵 可以既話搵街坊裝去做再tg報告<br />\n<br />\n第四. 衣著 希望大家唔理快閃定遊行 外套黑 底衫其他雜色 走佬時可以即時除 銀包手機任何個人身分證明文件跟身 袋同裝有需要即棄 唔好計較金錢<br />\n<br />\n第五. 近排大家好鐘意圍狗屋 但其實成效唔大 我建議狗宿舍 建制派議員屋企去快閃 會更好 話題性更大 同埋班狗難增援 而且佢怕你搞佢屋企人多過搞佢自己<br />\n<br />\n利申 快閃過都失敗過 比翻啲經驗大家參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab6bf9d3333cc63f68d4274b56a1be376417a88","tid":1536502,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"122647880734c82d5581b2ba5b6de44be5cd9169","tid":1536502,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5911583ad775d8001a865f126c6808b4013a0e0","tid":1536502,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:14:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首先佢要肯跳閘</span>"},{"pid":"7b3b6632a1efe0cfafe83df30aa6e54e68fa3536","tid":1536502,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:14:12.000Z","msg":"突然諗返菲律賓人質事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536383</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c44521aa8718c36287be3321f3170a5df44d4632","tid":1536502,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:15:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d7d983292e748ef3758cabf29c257e5b8592f7d","tid":1536502,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:15:03.000Z","msg":"入黎推啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05334b4330ed2ceaa44865491bfc348ba089e093","tid":1536502,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:15:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c4591c622627ddbba5938d2fc9f